column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid, p.ra, p.dec, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,   s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  w.w1mpro as w1 FROM wise_xmatch as xm   JOIN photoObjAll AS p on xm.sdss_objid = p.objid  JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN wise_allsky AS w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr WHERE   p.u BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.g BETWEEN # AND #
